<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Rokelin | Rediseño moderno</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #fff8ef;
      --bg-soft: #f7eadb;
      --dark: #22140f;
      --muted: #765f54;
      --red: #8f1d17;
      --red-dark: #66100c;
      --gold: #c8923f;
      --cream: #fffdf8;
      --border: rgba(34, 20, 15, .12);
      --shadow: 0 24px 70px rgba(34, 20, 15, .15);
      --radius: 28px;
    }

    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }

    html {
      scroll-behavior: smooth;
    }

    body {
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
      background: var(--bg);
      color: var(--dark);
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    a {
      color: inherit;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    img {
      max-width: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .container {
      width: min(1180px, calc(100% - 36px));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .topbar {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 13px;
    }

    .topbar .container {
      min-height: 38px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .topbar span {
      opacity: .86;
    }

    .topbar strong {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    header {
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 50;
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      background: rgba(255, 248, 239, .84);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    nav {
      min-height: 78px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .logo {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .06em;
    }

    .logo-mark {
      width: 44px;
      height: 44px;
      display: grid;
      place-items: center;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--red), var(--gold));
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(143, 29, 23, .25);
    }

    .logo small {
      display: block;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 11px;
      letter-spacing: .16em;
      margin-top: 2px;
    }

    .nav-links {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 26px;
      color: #4b352c;
      font-size: 15px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .nav-links a {
      position: relative;
    }

    .nav-links a::after {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
      bottom: -8px;
      width: 0;
      height: 2px;
      background: var(--red);
      transition: .25s ease;
    }

    .nav-links a:hover::after {
      width: 100%;
    }

    .nav-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 10px;
      min-height: 46px;
      padding: 0 20px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      font-weight: 800;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: transform .2s ease, box-shadow .2s ease, background .2s ease;
    }

    .btn:hover {
      transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--red);
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 16px 38px rgba(143, 29, 23, .25);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--red-dark);
    }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: #fff;
      border-color: var(--border);
      color: var(--dark);
    }

    .hero {
      position: relative;
      padding: 88px 0 70px;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: -220px -180px auto auto;
      width: 520px;
      height: 520px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: rgba(200, 146, 63, .24);
      filter: blur(10px);
      z-index: -1;
    }

    .hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.05fr .95fr;
      gap: 54px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 9px;
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(143, 29, 23, .08);
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(48px, 7vw, 86px);
      line-height: .95;
      letter-spacing: -.045em;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
    }

    .hero h1 span {
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .hero p {
      max-width: 620px;
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 18px;
      line-height: 1.75;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .hero-buttons {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 34px;
    }

    .hero-stats {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
      max-width: 620px;
    }

    .stat {
      padding: 18px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, .7);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .stat strong {
      display: block;
      font-size: 24px;
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .stat span {
      color: var(--muted);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-card {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 620px;
      border-radius: 42px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(34, 20, 15, .05), rgba(34, 20, 15, .72)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1604908176997-125f25cc6f3d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1100&q=80") center/cover;
    }

    .floating-card {
      position: absolute;
      left: 28px;
      right: 28px;
      bottom: 28px;
      padding: 26px;
      border-radius: 28px;
      background: rgba(255, 253, 248, .92);
      backdrop-filter: blur(18px);
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, .2);
    }

    .floating-card h3 {
      font-size: 26px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }

    .floating-card p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .badge-row {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 10px;
    }

    .badge {
      padding: 8px 12px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: var(--bg-soft);
      color: var(--red-dark);
      font-size: 13px;
      font-weight: 800;
    }

    section {
      padding: 82px 0;
    }

    .section-head {
      display: flex;
      align-items: end;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 36px;
    }

    .section-head h2 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(36px, 5vw, 58px);
      line-height: 1;
      letter-spacing: -.035em;
    }

    .section-head p {
      max-width: 510px;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.7;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 18px;
    }

    .feature {
      position: relative;
      min-height: 320px;
      padding: 28px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      justify-content: end;
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      overflow: hidden;
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(34, 20, 15, .12);
    }

    .feature::before {
      content: "";
      position: absolute;
      inset: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,.05), rgba(0,0,0,.74));
      z-index: 1;
    }

    .feature > * {
      position: relative;
      z-index: 2;
    }

    .feature h3 {
      font-size: 28px;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .feature p {
      opacity: .9;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .feature:nth-child(1) { background: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1615900128652-3f2035f1992f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80") center/cover; }
    .feature:nth-child(2) { background: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1555396273-367ea4eb4db5?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80") center/cover; }
    .feature:nth-child(3) { background: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1520607162513-77705c0f0d4a?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80") center/cover; }

    .products {
      background: var(--cream);
      border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .product-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 22px;
    }

    .product {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 30px;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 18px 42px rgba(34, 20, 15, .08);
      transition: transform .25s ease, box-shadow .25s ease;
    }

    .product:hover {
      transform: translateY(-8px);
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .product-img {
      height: 240px;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
    }

    .product:nth-child(1) .product-img { background-image: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1625944230945-1b7dd3b949ab?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"); }
    .product:nth-child(2) .product-img { background-image: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1607623814075-e51df1bdc82f?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"); }
    .product:nth-child(3) .product-img { background-image: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1559847844-5315695dadae?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"); }

    .product-content {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .product-content small {
      color: var(--gold);
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
    }

    .product-content h3 {
      margin: 9px 0 10px;
      font-size: 25px;
    }

    .product-content p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .price-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .price {
      font-size: 22px;
      font-weight: 900;
      color: var(--red);
    }

    .story-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: .9fr 1.1fr;
      gap: 46px;
      align-items: center;
    }

    .story-photo {
      min-height: 520px;
      border-radius: 38px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(143, 29, 23, .05), rgba(34, 20, 15, .45)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551218808-94e220e084d2?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1000&q=80") center/cover;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .timeline {
      display: grid;
      gap: 18px;
      margin-top: 28px;
    }

    .timeline-item {
      padding: 22px;
      border-radius: 24px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .timeline-item strong {
      color: var(--red);
      font-size: 20px;
    }

    .timeline-item p {
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-top: 6px;
    }

    .restaurant {
      background: var(--red);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 88px 0;
    }

    .restaurant .section-head p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.76);
    }

    .menu-list {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      gap: 14px;
    }

    .menu-item {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 18px;
      padding: 20px 22px;
      border-radius: 22px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.16);
    }

    .menu-item h4 {
      font-size: 17px;
      margin-bottom: 5px;
    }

    .menu-item span {
      color: #ffd99d;
      font-weight: 900;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .menu-item p {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.72);
      font-size: 14px;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    .cta {
      padding: 100px 0;
    }

    .cta-box {
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      border-radius: 40px;
      padding: 58px;
      background:
        linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(34,20,15,.92), rgba(34,20,15,.55)),
        url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1514933651103-005eec06c04b?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80") center/cover;
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    }

    .cta-box h2 {
      font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
      font-size: clamp(38px, 5vw, 64px);
      max-width: 700px;
      line-height: 1;
      margin-bottom: 18px;
    }

    .cta-box p {
      max-width: 560px;
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.78);
      line-height: 1.7;
      margin-bottom: 28px;
    }

    footer {
      background: var(--dark);
      color: #fff;
      padding: 44px 0;
    }

    .footer-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.2fr repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 34px;
    }

    footer h4 {
      margin-bottom: 12px;
      color: var(--gold);
    }

    footer p, footer a {
      color: rgba(255,255,255,.68);
      line-height: 1.8;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .mobile-menu {
      display: none;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 14px;
      padding: 10px 12px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    @media (max-width: 920px) {
      .nav-links, .nav-actions {
        display: none;
      }

      .mobile-menu {
        display: inline-flex;
      }

      .hero-grid,
      .story-grid,
      .footer-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .hero-card {
        min-height: 480px;
      }

      .feature-grid,
      .product-grid,
      .menu-list {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .section-head {
        display: block;
      }

      .section-head p {
        margin-top: 16px;
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 620px) {
      .topbar .container {
        justify-content: center;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .topbar span:last-child {
        display: none;
      }

      .hero {
        padding-top: 54px;
      }

      .hero-stats {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }

      .floating-card {
        left: 16px;
        right: 16px;
        bottom: 16px;
      }

      .cta-box {
        padding: 36px 24px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="topbar">
    <div class="container">
      <span>Jamón y productos de Teruel con envío online</span>
      <span><strong>Tel.</strong> 978 611 869 · rokelin@rokelin.com</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <header>
    <nav class="container">
      <a href="#" class="logo" aria-label="Rokelin">
        <span class="logo-mark">R</span>
        <span>ROKELIN <small>PURO CERDO</small></span>
      </a>

      <div class="nav-links">
        <a href="#historia">Empresa</a>
        <a href="#productos">Tienda</a>
        <a href="#restaurantes">Restaurantes</a>
        <a href="#exportacion">Exportación</a>
        <a href="#contacto">Contacto</a>
      </div>

      <div class="nav-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#productos">Ver productos</a>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#contacto">Comprar ahora</a>
      </div>

      <button class="mobile-menu" onclick="document.body.classList.toggle('menu-open')">Menú</button>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container hero-grid">
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Desde Teruel al mundo</div>
          <h1>Tradición turolense con sabor <span>premium.</span></h1>
          <p>
            Una propuesta renovada para Rokelin: más visual, más elegante y más enfocada a vender producto,
            contar historia y llevar al usuario hacia tienda, restaurantes y contacto sin perder la esencia artesanal.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-buttons">
            <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#productos">Descubrir selección</a>
            <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#historia">Conocer la historia</a>
          </div>
          <div class="hero-stats">
            <div class="stat"><strong>1975</strong><span>Origen familiar</span></div>
            <div class="stat"><strong>D.O.P.</strong><span>Jamón de Teruel</span></div>
            <div class="stat"><strong>360º</strong><span>Tienda, restauración y exportación</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="hero-card" aria-label="Jamón y gastronomía de Teruel">
          <div class="floating-card">
            <h3>Jamón curado en altura</h3>
            <p>Producto protagonista, presentación limpia y llamadas a la acción claras para mejorar la conversión.</p>
            <div class="badge-row">
              <span class="badge">Artesanal</span>
              <span class="badge">Teruel</span>
              <span class="badge">Selección gourmet</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="historia">
      <div class="container story-grid">
        <div class="story-photo"></div>
        <div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Nuestra historia</div>
          <div class="section-head" style="margin-bottom: 0; display: block;">
            <h2>Raíz familiar, mirada moderna.</h2>
            <p style="margin-top: 18px;">
              Rokelin nace como una marca turolense ligada a la charcutería tradicional y evoluciona hasta convertirse
              en una referencia en producto, restauración, franquicia y exportación.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="timeline">
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <strong>Origen</strong>
              <p>Una identidad cercana, familiar y muy vinculada al producto local.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <strong>Producto</strong>
              <p>Jamón D.O.P., embutidos y elaboraciones propias como eje principal de la marca.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="timeline-item">
              <strong>Expansión</strong>
              <p>Tienda online, restaurantes, franquicias y presencia internacional desde Teruel.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Qué ofrecemos</div>
            <h2>Tres caminos, una misma esencia.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>La web queda organizada para que el usuario entienda rápido dónde ir: comprar, reservar o conocer la marca.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="feature-grid">
          <a class="feature" href="#productos">
            <h3>Tienda online</h3>
            <p>Productos seleccionados, fichas claras y compra rápida.</p>
          </a>
          <a class="feature" href="#restaurantes">
            <h3>Restaurantes</h3>
            <p>Una experiencia gastronómica con platos tradicionales actualizados.</p>
          </a>
          <a class="feature" id="exportacion" href="#contacto">
            <h3>Exportación</h3>
            <p>Producto de Teruel preparado para llegar a nuevos mercados.</p>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="products" id="productos">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow">Nuestra selección</div>
            <h2>Productos estrella.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Tarjetas más visuales, con jerarquía clara, textos cortos y botón de compra directo.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="product-grid">
          <article class="product">
            <div class="product-img"></div>
            <div class="product-content">
              <small>Producto estrella</small>
              <h3>Jamón D.O.P.</h3>
              <p>Elaborado y curado en secadero propio. Ideal como producto principal de la tienda.</p>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price">6 - 8 kg</span>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Ver</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product">
            <div class="product-img"></div>
            <div class="product-content">
              <small>Selección gourmet</small>
              <h3>Caña de lomo</h3>
              <p>Elaborada con lomos seleccionados, perfecta para destacar en packs premium.</p>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price">Premium</span>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Ver</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="product">
            <div class="product-img"></div>
            <div class="product-content">
              <small>Más demandado</small>
              <h3>Longaniza de Aragón</h3>
              <p>Uno de los embutidos más reconocibles de la marca, con una presentación directa.</p>
              <div class="price-row">
                <span class="price">Artesanal</span>
                <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#">Ver</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="restaurant" id="restaurantes">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-head">
          <div>
            <div class="eyebrow" style="background: rgba(255,255,255,.12); color: #ffd99d;">Para recoger</div>
            <h2>Carta rápida y apetecible.</h2>
          </div>
          <p>Una sección de restaurante mucho más limpia, pensada para leer rápido desde móvil y pedir sin perderse.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="menu-list">
